Program: Great Lives
Title: Lise Meitner
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00pqjs9
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Oct 2017
Matthew Parris presents the biographical series in which his guests choose someone who has inspired their lives. Actress Jenny Agutter champions the life and work of pioneering Austrian physicist Lise Meitner, one of the scientists responsible for the discovery of nuclear fission.